  "title": "Medical Social Worker (Home Care)",
  "description": "<ul><li>Responsible for case work management involving systemic assessment and intervention for the well-being of patients and family members.</li><li>Perform referrals to other service providers and conducts home visit where necessary.</li><li>Work closely with multi-disciplinary team members.</li><li>Support projects and programmes.</li><li>Attend training and case work supervision.</li></ul><p><strong>Job Requirements:</strong></p><ul><li>Degree in Social Work or a Graduate Diploma in Social Work.</li><li>Registered with Singapore Association of Social Work.</li><li>Experience in means testing and healthcare setting is advantageous .</li><li>Salary range: $3400 - $5600</li><li>Working location: Toa Payoh</li><li>Working hours: Monday to Thursday: 8.00am to 5.30pm/Friday: 8.00am to 5.00pm</li></ul><p>Job ID: 7XYX853</p><p><br /></p><p><em><strong>All Successful candidates can expect a very competitive remuneration package and a comprehensive range of benefits.</strong></em></p><p><br /></p><p>Kindly email your resume in a detailed <strong>Word format</strong> to gesse.tan@peopleprofilers.com</p><p><br /></p><p>We regret that only shortlisted candidates will be notified</p><p><br /></p><p><strong>People Profilers Pte Ltd</strong></p><p>20 Cecil Street, #08-09, Plus Building, Singapore 049705</p><p>Tel: <a href=\"tel:69509745\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">69509745</a></p><p>EA Licence Number: 02C4944</p><p>EA Registration Number: R1108448</p><p>EA Personnel: Tan Lili Gesse</p>",
